### Test Categories API Endpoints

# Get all categories (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories?page=1&limit=10&active=true
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Create a new category (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Category",
  "description": "A test category for requisitions",
  "budgetCodes": ["TEST-001", "TEST-002"]
}

###

# Get category by ID (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/cat-001
Content-Type: application/json

###